data.description: You will be excited to call this home your own as soon as you see this great ranch plan. The home has great curb appeal with an upgraded stone archway that welcomes you on to the front porch where you can sit and have some morning coffee. Head on into the home where you will find LVP flooring throughout the home. This is a great floor plan with the primary and two secondary bedrooms on the main floor, a large family room that is open to kitchen with stunning white cabinetry and dark grey center island. The functional kitchen is graced with granite countertops, subway tile, stainless steel appliances and a butler's pantry. The back yard has a nice white privacy fence and a covered porch, great for those hot days while sipping on sweet tea. Ya'll better hurry and get to this one!
